WEBVTT

00:00:38.119 --> 00:00:40.936
Sister Jialin didn't dare tell my
brother directly when she got the news.

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:42.399
She asked me to tell you first.

00:01:03.560 --> 00:01:04.959
It's time.

00:01:38.079 --> 00:01:39.079
If you don't cry,

00:01:39.519 --> 00:01:40.519
she can pass on in peace.

00:01:47.600 --> 00:01:55.600
"A Winter Sun Wakes the Wind in Spring Hills' Dream"

00:01:59.600 --> 00:02:03.500
(Episode 6: Impermanence)

00:02:23.960 --> 00:02:24.960
Sister Lan,

00:02:26.319 --> 00:02:28.400
how could you keep me alive?

00:02:37.319 --> 00:02:38.319
Sister Lan,

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:41.520
how could you keep me alive?

00:02:43.360 --> 00:02:44.360
Sister Lan,

00:02:45.479 --> 00:02:47.680
how did I survive?

00:02:58.599 --> 00:02:59.599
Shi Yuhao,

00:03:01.520 --> 00:03:02.520
you murderer!

00:03:40.599 --> 00:03:41.759
Sister Lan's phone...

00:03:47.080 --> 00:03:49.400
Shi Yuhao made a video call to Sister Lan.

00:03:50.680 --> 00:03:52.520
He was screaming at her like a lunatic.

00:03:55.080 --> 00:03:58.800
Sister Lan spoke to him
calmly the entire time.

00:04:02.879 --> 00:04:05.159
I'm not sure what I saw back then.

00:04:07.199 --> 00:04:11.479
Suddenly, there was a white
shadow in the middle of the road.

00:04:13.879 --> 00:04:15.879
Sister Lan probably
thought it was a wild animal,

00:04:17.199 --> 00:04:18.199
so she swerved hard.

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:21.720
My vision blurred,

00:04:38.560 --> 00:04:40.319
and I didn't even have time to look.

00:04:49.360 --> 00:04:50.360
Brother,

00:04:52.079 --> 00:04:53.680
before you arrived,

00:04:54.319 --> 00:04:55.879
Sister Lan told the master

00:04:55.920 --> 00:04:57.280
that she wanted to be buried here.

00:04:57.680 --> 00:04:58.959
Right here in Xi Gui.

00:05:00.279 --> 00:05:02.159
But Sister Jialin disagreed,

00:05:02.160 --> 00:05:03.896
and she didn't believe
what the master said.

00:05:03.920 --> 00:05:06.279
Should you try to talk to Sister Jialin?

00:05:09.079 --> 00:05:11.000
No way. I'm taking her back.

00:05:11.120 --> 00:05:12.600
Tianyi is not her home.

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:14.199
I can't leave her here all alone.

00:05:14.279 --> 00:05:15.735
But this was Sister Lan's dying wish.

00:05:15.759 --> 00:05:16.958
This drama was also filmed here.

00:05:16.959 --> 00:05:18.336
I think Sister Lan would have wanted...

00:05:18.360 --> 00:05:19.360
Feng Qinglang!

00:05:20.920 --> 00:05:21.879
If it weren't for you,

00:05:21.880 --> 00:05:22.960
would Sister Lan have died?

00:05:26.519 --> 00:05:27.519
No.

00:05:28.160 --> 00:05:29.800
What right do you have to talk to me?

00:05:30.079 --> 00:05:31.879
I am Xing Lan's designated guardian.

00:05:32.160 --> 00:05:34.199
I have the right to decide where she rests.

00:05:34.399 --> 00:05:35.999
You have no right to make that decision.

00:06:53.279 --> 00:06:55.119
Brother Wenshu is
arriving in Xi Gui tomorrow.

00:07:04.759 --> 00:07:05.759
Changyang,

00:07:06.600 --> 00:07:09.000
are you serious about my brother?

00:07:18.759 --> 00:07:19.920
What do you think?

00:07:21.560 --> 00:07:22.959
It's hard to say.

00:07:24.680 --> 00:07:25.600
In my impression,

00:07:25.601 --> 00:07:28.560
you've always been a very
serious and reliable person.

00:07:29.920 --> 00:07:32.279
Two years ago, when
I first arrived in Molie,

00:07:32.519 --> 00:07:34.079
you cured my depression.

00:07:37.079 --> 00:07:38.559
But then you took my brother away,

00:07:38.560 --> 00:07:40.320
and he's been out of
touch for so many days.

00:07:41.680 --> 00:07:43.400
It's not a simple matter of right or wrong,

00:07:43.959 --> 00:07:45.480
but this is indeed very inappropriate.

00:07:51.720 --> 00:07:54.481
As long as Feng Qinglang's name
is still on the entertainment charts,

00:07:55.079 --> 00:07:57.360
his body does not belong to his soul.

00:08:32.720 --> 00:08:33.519
Brother,

00:08:33.679 --> 00:08:34.679
where is Qinglang?

00:08:34.720 --> 00:08:36.760
He got caught in the rain the day before
yesterday and has had a fever ever since.

00:08:36.799 --> 00:08:38.576
I shouldn't have told Sister
Lan the license plate number.

00:08:38.600 --> 00:08:39.919
I shouldn't have taken him away.

00:09:03.159 --> 00:09:04.399
I'll handle the funeral.

00:09:04.600 --> 00:09:05.720
You take good care of him.

00:09:13.919 --> 00:09:15.039
Where is Sister Lan's water?

00:09:15.519 --> 00:09:17.559
Where is Sister Lan's water?!

00:09:50.416 --> 00:09:55.389
[Sister Lan's tombstone

00:09:55.609 --> 00:10:00.870
[TN: The date of passing was 2032 which is
written according to the western calendar]

00:10:00.870 --> 00:10:05.003
[But the month and date are written using the
Earthly Branch system, which would make it June 6]

00:10:05.023 --> 00:10:08.309
[So why would you have a mix of two seperate
calendar systems engraved on a tombstone?]

00:10:08.333 --> 00:10:12.873
[Is the show implying some sort of calendrical
shift in the future? Or just a production error?]

00:10:12.923 --> 00:10:16.670
[These are the sorts of questions I have
watching long drawn out scenes like this.]

00:11:50.200 --> 00:11:52.535
Do you know how hard Sister
Lan worked to launch your career?

00:11:52.559 --> 00:11:53.759
Who doesn't have it hard?

00:11:55.080 --> 00:11:56.399
Sister Lan is dead.

00:11:57.159 --> 00:11:59.240
I'm just as sad as you are.

00:11:59.440 --> 00:12:02.399
Really? Does a murderer feel sad too?

00:12:03.559 --> 00:12:06.000
Please don't label me as a murderer.

00:12:06.799 --> 00:12:08.359
The time you video-called Sister Lan

00:12:08.360 --> 00:12:09.960
matches her time of death.

00:12:10.200 --> 00:12:11.479
But I wasn't at the scene.

00:12:11.480 --> 00:12:12.798
I wasn't driving the car.

00:12:12.799 --> 00:12:14.360
What makes you say I killed her?

00:12:14.600 --> 00:12:15.840
It was you, damn it!

00:12:19.960 --> 00:12:21.559
Do you know who you killed?

00:12:22.000 --> 00:12:23.400
She was the savior who rescued you!

00:12:25.879 --> 00:12:26.759
If you wanted to make a video call,

00:12:26.759 --> 00:12:27.200
if you wanted to scream at someone,

00:12:27.200 --> 00:12:28.080
you should have come at me!

00:12:28.080 --> 00:12:28.639
Come on!

00:12:28.639 --> 00:12:29.639
Come on!

00:12:30.879 --> 00:12:32.399
Do you think I wanted this to happen?

00:12:32.480 --> 00:12:33.679
Then why don't you go die?

00:12:34.080 --> 00:12:34.799
If my death

00:12:34.799 --> 00:12:35.559
could bring Sister Lan back,

00:12:35.560 --> 00:12:36.679
I would gladly die!

00:12:36.879 --> 00:12:38.799
Anyway, you've wanted
me dead for a long time,

00:12:39.759 --> 00:12:41.360
and nobody wants me alive anyway.

00:12:43.200 --> 00:12:45.360
Do you dare to admit
you killed Sister Lan?

00:12:48.159 --> 00:12:50.279
I do! You want to know, right?

00:12:50.600 --> 00:12:52.678
I called her and screamed at her.

00:12:52.679 --> 00:12:55.558
I asked her why she
released that old video.

00:12:55.559 --> 00:12:56.999
Why release it now when
she didn't back then?

00:12:57.023 --> 00:12:58.023
It's all damn hypocrisy!

00:12:58.080 --> 00:12:59.133
She deserved to crash!

00:12:59.157 --> 00:12:59.830
Fuck!

00:13:16.159 --> 00:13:18.360
We will let the police investigate this.

00:13:19.039 --> 00:13:20.799
Investigate? Go ahead and investigate!

00:13:21.200 --> 00:13:22.200
I'm not afraid!

00:13:53.010 --> 00:13:55.423
[Shi Yuhao: Go and investigate who put that old
video up. I believe it wasn't Sister Lan....

00:13:55.423 --> 00:13:57.076
[...and it couldn't have been you.]

00:13:57.156 --> 00:13:59.676
[Comments basically blaming
Sister Lan for her own death]

00:13:59.701 --> 00:14:03.496
[Slightly less rude comments
on the Weibo-like platform]

00:14:03.550 --> 00:14:26.130
[17 different posts saying "Sister
Lan Go Die" across both platforms]

00:14:51.559 --> 00:14:52.559
Yor fever broke.

00:15:42.279 --> 00:15:43.279
Changyang.

00:15:44.279 --> 00:15:46.720
I logged into the company's
cloud drive on your computer.

00:15:52.279 --> 00:15:53.480
I was the one who posted it.

00:15:58.759 --> 00:15:59.759
When?

00:16:01.720 --> 00:16:02.760
The day of the livestream,

00:16:02.799 --> 00:16:04.039
when Shi Yuhao joined the call.

00:16:10.200 --> 00:16:12.120
You think you did the
right thing, don't you?

00:16:13.879 --> 00:16:16.360
You can't just show mercy to wicked people.

00:16:26.919 --> 00:16:28.720
Sometimes you have
to take drastic measures.

00:16:29.759 --> 00:16:32.360
But did you get my permission
before using my knife?

00:16:33.919 --> 00:16:36.936
Sister Lan kept that video in the cloud
drive for seven years without posting it.

00:16:36.960 --> 00:16:38.720
If she really didn't want to post it,
why didn't she delete it?

00:16:39.320 --> 00:16:40.719
This was the trump card
Sister Lan left for you.

00:16:40.720 --> 00:16:42.360
It was meant to be played when necessary.

00:16:42.919 --> 00:16:44.839
Shi Yuhao was plotting
against you step by step.

00:16:44.919 --> 00:16:46.720
That was the best time to play this card.

00:16:55.600 --> 00:16:56.720
You are very rational.

00:16:58.120 --> 00:16:59.480
So rational that it terrifies me.

00:17:01.159 --> 00:17:02.879
No matter how justified your reasons were,

00:17:03.480 --> 00:17:05.000
you fired a random shot,

00:17:05.279 --> 00:17:06.839
and it killed the person closest to me.

00:17:07.000 --> 00:17:08.119
Calm down.

00:17:08.960 --> 00:17:10.160
No one killed Sister Lan.

00:17:10.519 --> 00:17:12.680
Don't get trapped in your own flawed logic.

00:17:15.119 --> 00:17:16.119
Fine.

00:17:16.759 --> 00:17:17.960
Then answer me this.

00:17:21.759 --> 00:17:23.639
Stealing videos from
someone else's cloud drive

00:17:24.160 --> 00:17:26.519
and uploading them without permission...

00:17:26.920 --> 00:17:27.960
is that illegal?

00:17:28.920 --> 00:17:30.358
Do you want to send everyone connected

00:17:30.359 --> 00:17:32.719
to Sister Lan's death
to prison? Is that it?

00:17:32.720 --> 00:17:33.720
Yes.

00:17:36.079 --> 00:17:39.119
If locking everyone up
could bring Sister Lan back,

00:17:39.519 --> 00:17:40.680
I'd go to prison too.

00:18:15.000 --> 00:18:17.680
I've always believed I'd
never regret anything I did.

00:18:19.440 --> 00:18:21.000
But now,

00:18:23.799 --> 00:18:25.920
I deeply regret meeting you.

00:20:23.400 --> 00:20:24.960
I only drink skim milk.

00:20:25.480 --> 00:20:26.520
It's been skimmed.

00:20:34.920 --> 00:20:35.960
You're up early.

00:20:58.119 --> 00:20:59.119
Mom

00:20:59.720 --> 00:21:01.760
I don't think the police
stand for justice anymore.

00:21:02.200 --> 00:21:04.640
There's no such thing as
absolute good or evil to begin with.

00:21:05.759 --> 00:21:07.479
It's my great honor to receive this award.

00:21:08.079 --> 00:21:09.880
Mom told me I shouldn't be surprised

00:21:10.119 --> 00:21:12.559
I just need to accept
everyone's recognition of me.

00:21:13.400 --> 00:21:14.440
Most of all

00:21:14.720 --> 00:21:18.559
I'd like to thank Ms. Xing Lan, who has
been like a mother to me in three lifetimes.

00:21:21.000 --> 00:21:22.759
When I won the award that year

00:21:23.960 --> 00:21:27.640
I talked about the shaman
priest's past-life origins on stage.

00:21:29.440 --> 00:21:33.000
Sister Lan chided me for
mentioning metaphysics in public.

00:21:35.599 --> 00:21:36.640
But I truly believe in

00:21:38.119 --> 00:21:40.680
our bond as mother and
son spanning three lifetimes.

00:21:46.880 --> 00:21:47.880
Mom

00:21:49.279 --> 00:21:51.720
The mother who accompanied
me through four lifetimes is gone.

00:21:53.519 --> 00:21:56.240
She just left a little earlier

00:21:57.000 --> 00:21:59.000
She's waiting for you in the next life.

00:21:59.799 --> 00:22:04.072
You'll share a fifth and sixth life
together in the cycle of rebirth.

00:23:19.986 --> 00:23:26.853
[Their motto:] "Don't place
your hopes on other people"

00:23:28.500 --> 00:23:30.996
President Fang, Kevin's side is refusing
to sign the supplementary contract.

00:23:31.020 --> 00:23:33.500
President Xing handled
this contract previously.

00:23:38.139 --> 00:23:39.379
I'll handle it.

00:23:39.619 --> 00:23:41.699
Post a Weibo update
using Qinglang's account.

00:23:41.980 --> 00:23:44.539
Find a scene with a
candle from his last drama,

00:23:44.540 --> 00:23:45.939
take a screenshot, and post it.

00:23:46.139 --> 00:23:47.139
Okay.

00:25:09.020 --> 00:25:10.220
Molie's tea...

00:25:14.740 --> 00:25:15.820
Do you dare to drink it?

00:25:28.500 --> 00:25:30.020
"With no hindrance in the mind,

00:25:30.500 --> 00:25:31.939
because there is no hindrance,

00:25:32.820 --> 00:25:34.139
there is no fear.

00:25:35.139 --> 00:25:37.139
Free from all distorted illusions,

00:25:37.899 --> 00:25:39.179
one reaches ultimate Nirvana."

00:25:50.699 --> 00:25:53.300
Brother Wenshu wants to
invite us to afternoon tea.

00:25:55.139 --> 00:25:56.220
You go.

00:25:57.820 --> 00:26:00.139
Just pass on whatever he has to say to me.

00:26:03.020 --> 00:26:04.020
Alright.

00:26:04.580 --> 00:26:07.139
I knew you wouldn't go. I'll go.

00:26:15.300 --> 00:26:18.179
Love you, my Best Actor brother! Haha!

00:26:18.419 --> 00:26:19.220
Yeah.

00:26:19.419 --> 00:26:20.939
This feels like a dramatic short play.

00:26:35.300 --> 00:26:37.581
I thought you'd take me to
a Michelin-starred restaurant.

00:26:39.540 --> 00:26:40.540
That's too formal.

00:26:41.300 --> 00:26:42.500
It would feel like a date.

00:26:43.179 --> 00:26:44.299
True.

00:26:44.300 --> 00:26:45.139
Since my brother isn't here,

00:26:45.140 --> 00:26:46.540
I don't get that kind of treatment.

00:26:47.500 --> 00:26:48.619
How is your brother?

00:26:49.500 --> 00:26:50.820
What do you think?

00:26:52.419 --> 00:26:55.820
I can picture him reciting scriptures.

00:26:56.699 --> 00:26:58.099
You know him too well.

00:27:07.806 --> 00:27:08.699
Brother Wenshu.

00:27:08.699 --> 00:27:09.540
Yes?

00:27:09.699 --> 00:27:11.419
I also blame myself for Sister Lan's death.

00:27:12.220 --> 00:27:14.020
If I hadn't brought my brother to Molie,

00:27:14.500 --> 00:27:16.139
none of this would have happened.

00:27:17.300 --> 00:27:18.500
I can't escape it either.

00:27:19.540 --> 00:27:21.620
I was the one who told
her the license plate number.

00:27:23.300 --> 00:27:25.139
So, who is the real culprit?

00:27:26.419 --> 00:27:27.579
It's as if we've all

00:27:27.580 --> 00:27:29.139
fallen into a murder game.

00:27:29.939 --> 00:27:31.020
Everything is tangled

00:27:31.300 --> 00:27:32.300
and interconnected.

00:27:34.139 --> 00:27:35.340
No one can be absolved.

00:27:35.540 --> 00:27:36.939
Everyone is a killer.

00:27:37.179 --> 00:27:40.139
Even the voices commenting online.

00:27:42.820 --> 00:27:45.139
Every word they spew is a lethal sword.

00:27:46.619 --> 00:27:49.939
And another killer is Sister Lan herself.

00:27:50.820 --> 00:27:52.060
She wanted to protect Qinglang,

00:27:52.980 --> 00:27:55.540
taking Qinglang's karma upon herself.

00:27:55.699 --> 00:27:58.020
It was a noble act, indeed.

00:27:58.699 --> 00:28:02.820
But she had to bear the
consequences of that karma.

00:28:08.899 --> 00:28:09.379
Tian.

00:28:09.379 --> 00:28:10.379
Yeah?

00:28:10.500 --> 00:28:12.339
Chen Zhu's family has accepted

00:28:12.340 --> 00:28:13.580
the caregiver I found for them.

00:28:14.540 --> 00:28:15.899
When his family isn't around,

00:28:15.939 --> 00:28:17.220
you can visit him anytime.

00:28:17.300 --> 00:28:18.139
Okay.

00:28:18.140 --> 00:28:20.139
I'll send you the caregiver's contact info.

00:28:21.340 --> 00:28:22.740
Thanks, Brother Wenshu.

00:28:23.780 --> 00:28:25.980
I'd like to pay you back for the caregiver.

00:28:29.540 --> 00:28:31.540
If it makes you feel better to pay me,

00:28:32.379 --> 00:28:33.500
then I'll take it.

00:28:36.340 --> 00:28:39.179
But honestly, it's your money anyway.

00:28:39.699 --> 00:28:41.300
You invest in my brother's movies,

00:28:41.500 --> 00:28:43.138
he makes money to support me,

00:28:43.139 --> 00:28:44.820
and then I give his money to you.

00:28:47.780 --> 00:28:49.099
Whatever makes you happy.

00:29:09.486 --> 00:29:13.511
[Post from Ji Zongjun: A human mother rescued
her child from a tiger cub's jaws.

00:29:14.302 --> 00:29:20.681
She was hailed as a great mother by other
humans. But the tiger cub lost its food and died.

00:29:21.091 --> 00:29:23.650
Every act of protection is based
solely on one's own perspective;

00:29:24.081 --> 00:29:26.259
judgements of right and wrong
are merely different viewpoints.

00:29:26.296 --> 00:29:30.543
But great mothers still
deserve our respect."

00:29:31.223 --> 00:29:32.303
Namaste."

00:29:43.659 --> 00:29:46.619
On the 3rd of next month, we're
shooting a spin-off for the last drama.

00:29:46.939 --> 00:29:48.059
We need you to make a cameo.

00:29:48.379 --> 00:29:49.499
This was also Sister Lan's...

00:29:49.500 --> 00:29:50.500
I'll do it.

00:29:55.540 --> 00:29:56.619
Let me handle this.

00:29:56.780 --> 00:29:58.300
Go pick out an outfit for Lang Di.

00:30:00.379 --> 00:30:01.780
Is this hair length okay?

00:30:03.939 --> 00:30:04.939
It's fine.

00:30:08.939 --> 00:30:09.939
Sister Jialin.

00:30:10.300 --> 00:30:12.540
If there's anything I can
do to help the company,

00:30:12.740 --> 00:30:14.020
just let me know.

00:30:16.379 --> 00:30:17.618
When Sister Lan was here,

00:30:17.619 --> 00:30:19.580
she never let you worry
about company matters.

00:30:20.540 --> 00:30:23.699
Now that she's gone, how
would I dare order you around?

00:30:24.899 --> 00:30:26.939
If it weren't to fulfill
Sister Lan's last wish,

00:30:27.179 --> 00:30:29.340
I wouldn't have asked
you to come this time.

00:30:31.699 --> 00:30:32.980
Is Brother Guo still not back?

00:30:34.340 --> 00:30:36.098
He has severe post-accident trauma.

00:30:36.099 --> 00:30:38.019
He still needs to undergo
treatment for a while.

00:30:39.220 --> 00:30:40.740
You and that Xu Changyang...

00:30:40.980 --> 00:30:41.980
It's over.

00:30:45.020 --> 00:30:47.419
Good. Don't cause any
more trouble for the company.

00:30:49.459 --> 00:30:50.459
Okay.

00:30:53.540 --> 00:30:54.540
Mm.

00:30:56.165 --> 00:30:57.646
I don't drink iced drinks.

00:30:57.980 --> 00:30:59.379
Oh, I forgot.

00:31:01.260 --> 00:31:02.980
Who is Lang Di playing in this drama?

00:31:04.619 --> 00:31:06.540
My uncle, Feng Jianqiu.

00:31:06.740 --> 00:31:07.740
I see.

00:31:08.659 --> 00:31:10.458
Our drama has nothing to
do with the Republican era.

00:31:10.459 --> 00:31:11.699
Why is the spin-off about this?

00:31:12.459 --> 00:31:14.619
Our company owns the rights to this novel.

00:31:14.980 --> 00:31:16.260
We might adapt it in the future,

00:31:16.540 --> 00:31:18.500
so they had us shoot a
few concept teasers first.

00:31:18.780 --> 00:31:20.339
You're pretty high up in your company, huh?

00:31:20.340 --> 00:31:21.340
You know everything.

00:31:22.260 --> 00:31:23.780
It isn't a secret anyway.

00:31:25.939 --> 00:31:27.899
Our company would
never tell us things like this.

00:31:29.740 --> 00:31:31.659
Lang Di...

00:31:36.379 --> 00:31:37.580
He has no ego at all.

00:31:38.419 --> 00:31:40.019
Lang Di has always had a great work ethic.

00:31:40.020 --> 00:31:41.980
I was his temporary
assistant for a few months.

00:31:42.020 --> 00:31:43.060
He's a really nice guy.

00:31:43.659 --> 00:31:44.659
Camera rolling.

00:31:45.459 --> 00:31:46.619
Okay, camera rolling.

00:31:47.540 --> 00:31:49.780
Three, two, one, action!

00:31:50.659 --> 00:31:53.220
Feng Jianqiu, where did
you take my son this time?

00:31:59.780 --> 00:32:00.780
Cut!

00:32:01.419 --> 00:32:02.419
Cut!

00:32:05.780 --> 00:32:08.060
Lang Di, can we try a different vibe?

00:32:08.260 --> 00:32:09.900
Sure, Director. What do you have in mind?

00:32:10.340 --> 00:32:12.540
Feng Jianqiu is more
cynical and irreverant.

00:32:13.226 --> 00:32:14.305
Okay, I get it.

00:32:14.340 --> 00:32:15.379
Alright, great.

00:32:17.139 --> 00:32:18.378
Everyone, get ready.

00:32:18.379 --> 00:32:19.540
Let's do another take.

00:32:21.740 --> 00:32:22.740
Camera rolling.

00:32:23.379 --> 00:32:24.379
Rolling.

00:32:25.419 --> 00:32:27.740
Three, two, one, action!

00:32:28.139 --> 00:32:30.139
Feng Jianqiu, where is my son?

00:32:30.419 --> 00:32:31.939
Where did you put him?

00:32:38.659 --> 00:32:40.580
Cut! We got it.

00:32:49.020 --> 00:32:50.580
He really is handsome.

00:34:06.260 --> 00:34:07.378
Lang Di, what would you like to drink?

00:34:07.379 --> 00:34:08.379
I'll go get it.

00:34:09.540 --> 00:34:10.980
I brought tea in my car.

00:34:11.260 --> 00:34:12.260
Okay.

00:34:16.580 --> 00:34:17.220
Oh, thank you.

00:34:17.221 --> 00:34:18.260
I'll do it myself.

00:34:18.619 --> 00:34:19.379
Uh, let me know if you need anything.

00:34:19.379 --> 00:34:20.379
I'll get back to work.

00:34:42.780 --> 00:34:44.020
Are you coming home for dinner?

00:34:44.740 --> 00:34:46.540
No, I'm on set.

00:34:47.139 --> 00:34:50.379
Let me ask you, the tea you
brought me over the last two years...

00:34:50.419 --> 00:34:51.859
was it all from Teacher Fu?

00:34:52.300 --> 00:34:53.300
Why do you ask?

00:34:53.980 --> 00:34:54.980
Just answer me.

00:34:55.699 --> 00:34:57.618
How could I remember
with so many kinds of tea?

00:34:57.619 --> 00:34:58.659
Some were from Teacher Fu.

00:35:00.379 --> 00:35:02.459
What about the ripe tea?
Who sent the ripe tea?

00:35:03.060 --> 00:35:04.300
That must have been Changyang.

00:35:05.060 --> 00:35:06.539
His ripe tea is as filling as a meal.

00:35:06.540 --> 00:35:07.756
You won't feel hungry after drinking it.

00:35:07.780 --> 00:35:09.499
I usually keep some on hand too.

00:35:09.500 --> 00:35:10.940
I drink it when I can't eat on time.

00:35:23.500 --> 00:35:25.740
He fulfilled his childhood dream.

00:35:26.179 --> 00:35:28.659
Starting from meeting
the one he loved at sixteen,

00:35:28.899 --> 00:35:31.659
all the way to twenty-six, thirty-six,

00:35:31.980 --> 00:35:33.980
and finally to one hundred and sixteen.

00:35:34.540 --> 00:35:35.540
One hundred years.

00:35:35.780 --> 00:35:39.355
Spending a hundred seasons of spring, summer,
autumn, and winter with his love in this world...

00:35:39.379 --> 00:35:41.500
that's a legendary kind of happiness.

00:35:42.260 --> 00:35:43.260
By his calculations,

00:35:43.459 --> 00:35:45.299
I'll have to live to one
hundred and eighteen.

00:35:47.980 --> 00:35:48.980
By his calculations,

00:35:49.619 --> 00:35:51.459
I'll have to live to one
hundred and eighteen.

00:35:52.939 --> 00:35:53.939
One hundred years.

00:35:55.500 --> 00:35:59.300
Spending a hundred seasons of spring, summer,
autumn, and winter with his love in this world...

00:35:59.740 --> 00:36:01.859
that's a legendary kind of happiness.

00:36:29.139 --> 00:36:31.459
You're a hard superstar to
book. What are we eating?

00:36:32.179 --> 00:36:33.179
I'm skipping dinner tonight.

00:36:33.180 --> 00:36:34.379
I brought my own tea.

00:36:35.139 --> 00:36:36.540
We're at a Western restaurant,

00:36:36.580 --> 00:36:37.740
and you brought your own tea?

00:36:39.580 --> 00:36:40.740
Save that money

00:36:40.859 --> 00:36:41.979
and invest in my next movie.

00:36:43.256 --> 00:36:44.036
Qingtian?

00:36:44.060 --> 00:36:46.059
You're his brother, and you're asking me?

00:36:46.180 --> 00:36:47.380
I'm not as responsible as you.

00:36:48.820 --> 00:36:50.220
He went to see Chen Zhu.

00:36:50.859 --> 00:36:53.939
He's going to the hospital
for a checkup this week,

00:36:54.379 --> 00:36:55.739
so Qingtian has a chance to visit.

00:36:56.820 --> 00:36:58.740
That's why we're sneaking out to meet up.

00:36:59.419 --> 00:37:00.579
What a strange dynamic.

00:37:02.820 --> 00:37:04.140
Will Chen Zhu ever wake up?

00:37:04.740 --> 00:37:07.579
It's been three years
without any improvement.

00:37:08.260 --> 00:37:11.140
His family delayed his
treatment in the first year.

00:37:13.019 --> 00:37:14.740
I really feel sorry for my brother.

00:37:16.379 --> 00:37:18.859
I should play a comatose
patient in my next movie. It's easy.

00:37:19.859 --> 00:37:21.260
And let Changyang take care of you?

00:37:22.019 --> 00:37:23.180
Why bring him up?

00:37:23.939 --> 00:37:25.819
You can drink his tea
but can't talk about him?

00:37:29.140 --> 00:37:32.660
By the way, I asked Qingtian to take
me to the coffee plantation in Molie.

00:37:32.939 --> 00:37:33.939
Want to come along?

00:37:34.180 --> 00:37:35.180
I'm not going.

00:37:35.939 --> 00:37:37.099
Changyang isn't here anymore.

00:37:40.939 --> 00:37:42.099
Just ask if you want to know.

00:37:43.220 --> 00:37:44.260
He went home.

00:37:45.220 --> 00:37:47.859
My dad made him go
home to study for his exams.

00:37:48.740 --> 00:37:49.859
Do you all live together?

00:37:50.459 --> 00:37:51.459
Not really.

00:37:52.539 --> 00:37:54.979
Changyang lives with his mom and sister,

00:37:55.379 --> 00:37:56.419
but it's not far.

00:37:56.620 --> 00:37:57.660
Just one building away.

00:38:01.579 --> 00:38:02.979
My dad has a sensitive status.

00:38:03.939 --> 00:38:06.579
You must keep our family
matters strictly confidential.

00:38:07.220 --> 00:38:09.460
No matter how sensitive,
it's not as high-profile as me.

00:38:10.220 --> 00:38:12.820
You've got it good with
your foreign citizenship.

00:38:13.459 --> 00:38:17.260
Legally transferring family
wealth abroad. Clever move.

00:38:18.180 --> 00:38:19.500
When you can't get what you want,

00:38:20.780 --> 00:38:22.180
no amount of money matters.

00:38:24.379 --> 00:38:26.939
After we eat, come with
me to pick up Qingtian.

00:38:28.140 --> 00:38:29.140
Okay.

00:38:37.379 --> 00:38:38.779
Ugh, here you go again.

00:38:38.780 --> 00:38:40.180
You shameless bitch!

00:38:47.459 --> 00:38:49.578
Run faster! If I see you again,

00:38:49.579 --> 00:38:51.299
I'll scald you to death with boiling water!

00:38:52.180 --> 00:38:52.859
Seducing my son...

00:38:52.860 --> 00:38:54.260
You half-man, half-woman freak!

00:41:40.539 --> 00:41:41.539
Here!

00:41:50.939 --> 00:41:52.419
Was your date a success?

00:41:54.859 --> 00:41:55.859
Yes, it was.

00:42:05.579 --> 00:42:06.780
How is Chen Zhu?

00:42:07.260 --> 00:42:08.379
Quite stable.

00:42:15.059 --> 00:42:16.740
Let's go, the car is over there.

00:42:20.820 --> 00:42:22.419
Are you going to Molie with Wenshu?

00:42:23.539 --> 00:42:26.059
He wants to visit a coffee
plantation, so I'm accompanying him.

00:42:26.340 --> 00:42:28.260
After all, he did me a huge favor.

00:42:31.419 --> 00:42:33.939
Being able to see Chen
Zhu is indeed a huge favor.

00:42:37.399 --> 00:42:38.839
I don't want to talk
about that with you.

00:42:48.180 --> 00:42:49.180
Tian.

00:42:49.939 --> 00:42:51.339
Chen Zhu is never going to wake up.

00:43:03.740 --> 00:43:04.740
Brother.

00:43:05.979 --> 00:43:07.620
If you love someone,

00:43:08.820 --> 00:43:10.340
would you give up on him?

00:43:20.019 --> 00:43:21.779
I don't want to see you
pretend to be happy.

00:43:26.539 --> 00:43:27.939
I've accepted it.

00:43:46.340 --> 00:43:49.379
The brand wants to record an
extra commercial tomorrow morning.

00:43:49.579 --> 00:43:51.620
Sister Jialin said we're
all staying here tonight

00:43:51.660 --> 00:43:53.060
and heading back together tomorrow.

00:43:53.939 --> 00:43:55.939
Your company has been notified.

00:43:57.419 --> 00:43:58.538
Brother Guo isn't here tonight.

00:43:58.539 --> 00:44:00.019
Can I share a room with Han Lu?

00:44:00.740 --> 00:44:01.780
I'll arrange it.

00:44:01.939 --> 00:44:02.939
Thanks, Sister.

00:44:13.579 --> 00:44:15.620
I can't share a room with you tonight.

00:44:16.260 --> 00:44:17.660
Then who do you want to sleep with?

00:44:19.379 --> 00:44:20.579
I'm not sleeping.

00:44:21.379 --> 00:44:22.379
Not sleeping?

00:44:23.539 --> 00:44:24.740
Even better.

00:44:47.140 --> 00:44:49.019
Go get the key card from Sister Coco.

00:44:49.740 --> 00:44:50.740
No.

00:44:54.419 --> 00:44:55.740
There are cameras here.

00:44:56.740 --> 00:44:57.780
So what if there are?

00:45:02.780 --> 00:45:03.579
Hey.

00:45:03.579 --> 00:45:04.379
Qi Haoyu.

00:45:04.380 --> 00:45:07.179
You just mess around the moment
no one's watching you on set, huh?

00:45:07.180 --> 00:45:08.859
The crew's behind-the-scenes team...

00:45:09.140 --> 00:45:11.259
is always waiting to snap
photos with their phones.

00:45:11.260 --> 00:45:12.458
Are you out of your mind?

00:45:12.459 --> 00:45:13.260
What's wrong?

00:45:13.261 --> 00:45:14.539
What's wrong?

00:45:14.820 --> 00:45:15.660
You were caught on camera.

00:45:15.661 --> 00:45:17.418
Fang Jialin wants to release
the behind-the-scenes footage.

00:45:17.419 --> 00:45:18.978
Their agency doesn't care if
their artists ruin themselves,

00:45:18.979 --> 00:45:20.220
but I have to care about you!

00:45:20.539 --> 00:45:21.699
You mess around with guys too?

00:45:21.700 --> 00:45:23.220
Are you that desperate?

00:45:23.379 --> 00:45:24.740
I wasn't messing around.

00:45:25.220 --> 00:45:26.019
Not messing around?

00:45:26.020 --> 00:45:27.140
Are you serious then?

00:45:27.740 --> 00:45:29.180
Would you actually dare to date him?

00:45:30.019 --> 00:45:31.259
What did your teacher tell you?

00:45:31.260 --> 00:45:32.498
You're supposed to star in serious dramas.

00:45:32.499 --> 00:45:33.899
Take the respectable path, damn it.

00:45:34.579 --> 00:45:36.395
Then why did you make me
take this role in the first place?

00:45:36.419 --> 00:45:37.899
Cut the crap and stop making excuses.

00:45:38.260 --> 00:45:39.378
If you want to survive in showbiz,

00:45:39.379 --> 00:45:40.180
keep it in your pants

00:45:40.181 --> 00:45:41.261
and keep your pants zipped.

00:46:24.539 --> 00:46:25.539
Cut!

00:46:35.979 --> 00:46:36.979
Qi Haoyu.

00:46:38.979 --> 00:46:40.140
Don't talk to me.

00:46:43.379 --> 00:46:44.740
Your agency chewed you out.

00:46:44.780 --> 00:46:45.939
Why take it out on me?

00:46:47.140 --> 00:46:47.979
I told you,

00:46:47.979 --> 00:46:48.620
don't talk to me.

00:46:48.620 --> 00:46:49.620
Do you not understand?

00:46:50.660 --> 00:46:51.660
You're crazy.

00:47:57.820 --> 00:48:01.740
The white-haired
burying the black-haired...

00:48:06.459 --> 00:48:07.740
I gave the wrong gift.

00:48:10.459 --> 00:48:11.459
Brother Guo,

00:48:12.939 --> 00:48:14.820
his hat is white,

00:48:15.019 --> 00:48:16.419
not his hair.

00:48:30.180 --> 00:48:31.180
At that moment,

00:48:32.018 --> 00:48:33.018
whoosh!

00:48:33.220 --> 00:48:35.620
A white deer suddenly appeared ahead.

00:48:39.180 --> 00:48:40.620
It was stark white,

00:48:41.379 --> 00:48:42.939
glowing with white light.

00:48:44.260 --> 00:48:47.660
It was so blinding that Sister
Lan and I had to shut our eyes.

00:48:49.140 --> 00:48:51.220
Then, the white deer suddenly bellowed,

00:48:53.939 --> 00:48:54.939
"Halt!"

00:48:55.740 --> 00:48:57.260
"I shall blind you!"

00:49:10.579 --> 00:49:12.379
What era of performance art is this?

00:49:13.379 --> 00:49:15.019
A '90s storytelling show.

00:49:18.059 --> 00:49:19.819
Brother Guo must have
traveled back in time.

00:49:27.045 --> 00:49:28.925
No one else could have done it.

00:49:29.056 --> 00:49:30.729
"The Ferryman 3: Endless Love"

00:49:31.780 --> 00:49:34.820
I don't even know how
Sister Lan managed to do it.

00:49:37.660 --> 00:49:39.379
She kept me alive.

00:49:42.180 --> 00:49:44.780
Isn't self-preservation human instinct?

00:50:49.300 --> 00:50:51.099
You can skip other events,

00:50:51.100 --> 00:50:55.019
but you must attend Hot
Love's 7th anniversary gala.

00:50:56.700 --> 00:50:58.499
Okay.

00:51:47.220 --> 00:51:49.858
Now, let's welcome Hot Love's...

00:51:49.859 --> 00:51:51.939
brand ambassador, Feng Qinglang!

00:52:00.660 --> 00:52:03.019
Today marks our brand's 7th anniversary.

00:52:03.140 --> 00:52:06.379
Qinglang, is there anything
you'd like to say to Hot Love?

00:52:12.260 --> 00:52:13.340
Happy birthday.

00:52:14.260 --> 00:52:17.340
What a heartfelt wish!

00:52:22.859 --> 00:52:25.939
With that cold face, you clearly
doesn't want to renew your contract.

00:52:56.019 --> 00:52:57.019
Try this.

00:53:00.180 --> 00:53:01.620
Why did you show up without warning?

00:55:22.820 --> 00:55:24.220
Which room is Changyang staying in?

00:55:24.859 --> 00:55:25.859
He's gone.

00:55:28.379 --> 00:55:29.379
Where did he go?

00:55:29.579 --> 00:55:30.579
Back to Tianyi.

00:55:30.859 --> 00:55:32.659
He went to discuss a
project with Teacher Fu.

00:55:34.740 --> 00:55:36.260
You sure know a lot.

00:55:36.899 --> 00:55:38.300
I'm with him right now.

00:55:39.300 --> 00:55:41.220
If you need him, I can pass him the phone.